Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alibi tricks are always uncovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun shines brightly and warmly like it knows no limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can also nurture a surprising case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what you said on the phone last night, I think I understand the situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Seizan-sensei really in that much of a slump?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he hasn't drawn a single thing in the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he is a 70-year-old man, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he can't picture things clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stress got to him, and as a result his hands have started shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:18.42,Top,,0,0,0,,Kuroki Jirou (28)\NSeozam's Apprentice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be hard to bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately, he refuses to eat much and gets really moody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes he'll get really agitated, and other times, he'll refuse to speak a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now he wants to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:44.20,Top,,0,0,0,,PLACE EXPOSED TO THE SUN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought you out here today because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might cheer Sensei up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you when you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:03:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem—I'm always happy to help one of my old drinking buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he heard that an inn with hot springs and alcohol were prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just couldn't refuse—right, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sensei sure is lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have a student as thoughtful as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to him that I can accomplish so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nightingale!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They live in the bamboo forest around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming from over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seizan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How delightful we are, to meet friends from afar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you came to visit on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw the station I was at, your image suddenly popped out of my head, so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you are well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:01.15,Top,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa Seizan (70)\NJapanese Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say I'm as lively as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just about to sketch the bamboos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't appear to be on the verge of suicide at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's putting up an act so he doesn't look bad in front of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An act, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what's called a "nightingale's echoing song."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, they chirp like that when they're distressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be gone soon, so please forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is special to the nightingales, and must be cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's depart, so as not to disturb them any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.33,Top,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto Noriko (35)\NHayakawa Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Seizan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have visitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you prepare something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's Seizan-sensei's housekeeper, Yamamoto Noriko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this—it's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother can't look after him because she came down with a fever, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you never to bring kids here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send him home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never let me see his face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take him home, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, is that a new piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful drawing of Mt Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a drawing I did recently at a client's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Kuroki-san, do you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you became Sensei's apprentice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw some of his work before, it was quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike Seizan-sensei's, it was very colorful, ight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're chromatic paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, isn't that art competition that you're presiding over starting soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're certainly well informed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deadline for it is the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san, why don't you enter too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I've seen, I'm sure you'll do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do, people will mock me, your teacher, Hayakawa Seizan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki isn't skilled enough to participate yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, but, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as he says, Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still lack practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it, Ran-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you model for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that lean practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san, wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei—can you draw her, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were in Tokyo, you used to draw something for us on the fly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, tonight is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop, Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would always draw while drunk before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't been able to take in alcohol like I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, how about we go fishing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san's group can come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored if you would join us, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fishing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't gone in quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the rain be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The forecast said that it should let up early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll be going to bed for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a good night, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, how could you be so rude to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me, Kuroki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to test his drawing abilities to see if you were really right about him, so I put up an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is where you work, Kuroki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make it, Kuroki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not finished, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The colors are really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I use these powder paints to make my colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This white one is called "whitewash, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The powder is made from crushing oyster shells to tiny pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oysters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Nightingale's echoing song," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get much sleep because I was caring for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm off to get a doctor to examine her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei hasn't woken up yet, so go ahead to the pier without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seizan-sensei is not joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems like he's relaxing in the house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I'm giving the phone to Mouri-san now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll have to pass for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we come check—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look forward to our big catches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's best to leave him alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old boot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Kuroki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A note...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can't draw anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry for relying on you—thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems t at a suicide note was found when the maid went to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact the police right away and have them search the nearby area!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hearthat, Yamamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be there as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seizan-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou, a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Daimatsu from the precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since a note was found, this is almost certainly a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably tied the rope to the bamboo and jumped from the rock to strangle himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is from 11:00 to 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just about the time we were fishing, he tied the rope to the bamboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are these other bamboo poles cut down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there's no water in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were probably cut this morning, after the rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go play somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's way too soon to call this suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is Seizan-sensei's atelier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seizan-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IHtmust have been trying to draw it rightth iswhole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bamboo journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.84,Top,,0,0,0,,April 10th (Sunny), bamboo sprout grew 30 cm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.13,Top,,0,0,0,,April 11th (Sunny), bamboo sprout grew 60 cm - incredibly fast
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.09,Top,,0,0,0,,April 12th (Sunny), the sprout grew 2 meters probably due to the rain last night - bamboos do shoot up after a rain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.72,Top,,0,0,0,,He's been documenting the growth of the bamboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's like this, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are expensive paintings here, so quit scampering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sketch of Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just about to say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've taken their statements, so I was just about to report to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's too soon to call this a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, Sensei said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is special to the nightingales, and must be cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think that a man like that would kill himself in that forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, after dinner, he went to his room to continue drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably intended to give this to us as a present when we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think someone like that would commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a murder disguised as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The so-called "nightingale's echoing song" is because they are alerted by intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning, heard the nightingales chirp right before seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then rushed by, looking rather pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to have been in the forest during that time, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the time of death was between 11:00 AM and 1:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has an alibi for that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a great hospital, so I took my mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san's painting is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he worked on it all last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:16:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-neechan, Uncle asked for you to bring him this sketchbook and the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was always with her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that your alibi has held up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I guess Sensei really did commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daimatsu-san, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seizan-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit tried to disguise it as suicide, but it was actually murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The motive lies in this picture brought by Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san, you planned to enter tomorrow's contest with this painting, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Sensei would never allow this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:17:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you thought of a way to murder him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that Sensei was in a slump due to his inability to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to cheer him up, you called me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei wasn't really depressed, nor did he have a reason to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his hands would shake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the drawing of Mt Fuji in the guest room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he had drawn it recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, by following his rough sketch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who finished the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of his works from the past few years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're really your drawings, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's w y the idea of entering the contest and standing on your own two feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are pretty detrimental to Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, you suddenly asked Ran to be your model in order to induce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that dad would take the opportunity to find out whether or not Seizan-sensei really couldn't draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing his condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san, I believed what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thought it wouldn't be strange if he did commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kuroki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Early this morning, you brought him to the clearing in the forest, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong—you talked to him yourself while he was on the phone, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you had to do was obtain a recording of his voice beforehand and set it to play as his answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, like I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, that you were out with us on the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, show Daimatsu-san the sketchbook that I had Conan give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bamboo in this forest actually grows a lot faster than I first thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us how much it grew on the third day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around two meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bamboo shoot began to sprout from yesterday's rain, and when the temperature rose it grew extraordinarily fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used that fact to murder Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Early this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gave Sensei sleeping pills and carried him into the clearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you sat Sensei in front of the bamboo shoot that you chose, and tied a rope around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then cut away all the surrounding plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the bamboo that you tied to the rope would get a lot of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning, we heard the nightingales chirping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, Kuroki-san, was because they were alerted by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the sun came out, the bamboo continued to grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And eventually strangled Seizan-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This explains how you were able to kill Sensei while fishing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The white stuff on your feet is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just whitewash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't prove anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That isn't whitewash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the remnants left from the bamboo that you cut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, sawdust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been behind all of Sensei's drawings for the past few years, as per his order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to receive the credit for my own works instead of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it was only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted them to bask in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted someone to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't you know anything about modern art?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you call that modern art? It's just a child's doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Conan-kun is way better...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't compare me to a brat like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just don't understand sophisticated taste in art!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I don't.
